        {
            "title": "上善黃金曾瀉近23%  大股東近8.1%持股遭斬倉",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上善黃金(01939)今早大挫，最低見1.19元，瀉22.73%，現跌9.09%，報1.4元，最高見1.7元，成交2370萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"設計圖片。巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/bplib_20250916-180047_2025施政報告_財經_港交所-13_source-bp_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"設計圖片。巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/bplib_20250916-180047_2025施政報告_財經_港交所-13_source-bp_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">設計圖片。巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上善黃金昨天中午公布，控股股東兼主席黃仕坤減持8.09%股權，至下午近七時公司發補充公告，稱黃仕坤確認出售事項是由融資人以場內強制出售方式進行，出售就保證金性質融資存放於證券帳戶的股份</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團指，據黃仕坤作查詢後所知，概不會有進一步以強制出售方式出售他所控制的股份。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15481958-%e4%b8%8a%e5%96%84%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e6%9b%be%e7%80%89%e8%bf%9123-%e5%a4%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e8%bf%918-1%e6%8c%81%e8%82%a1%e9%81%ad%e6%96%ac%e5%80%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/01939-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 11:20:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息升  樓按相關拆息升15點子  重上三厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15479505&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息向上，與樓按相關的一個月拆息報3.03482厘，升15.024基點，連升兩日，是11月28日後最高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映銀行資金成本的三個月拆息報3.03458厘，升2.631基點。<br/> <br/>   隔夜息報2.06821厘，升59.309基點；一周拆息升40.571基點，報2.1厘，兩周則升34.845基點，報2.22643厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長息方面，六個月拆息跌1.601基點，報3.10113厘，一年期則跌2.273基點，報3.1481厘。<br/> </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479505-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%8d%87-%e6%a8%93%e6%8c%89%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%8d%8715%e9%bb%9e%e5%ad%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20250916_fi_bank_fb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 11:10:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "投資客858萬購現崇山2房戶收租  2011年買入現帳賺近180萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15479387&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">利嘉閣地產新啟德-現崇山分行促成黃大仙現崇山5B座中層D室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約523方呎，屬2房間隔，向西南，望內園。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新買家為投資客，計劃購入單位作長線收租，議價後以858萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約16,405元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，原業主於2011年以約678.8萬元一手購入單位，持貨至今轉售，現帳面獲利約179萬元，期內物業升值約26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該屋苑目前約有40個單位放賣，最低入場費由約850萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479387-%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e5%ae%a2858%e8%90%ac%e8%b3%bc%e7%8f%be%e5%b4%87%e5%b1%b12%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6%e6%94%b6%e7%a7%9f-2011%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%b7%e5%85%a5%e7%8f%be%e5%b8%b3%e8%b3%ba%e8%bf%91180%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 11:10:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "馬鞍山銀湖．天峰2房 零議價以760萬元獲用家承接",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15479361&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產馬鞍山迎海御峰分行表示，馬鞍山銀湖．天峰最新錄3座低層G室，建築面積728平方呎，實用面積556平方呎，2房間隔，開價約760萬元，日前零議價易手，實用平均呎價13669元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新買家為用家，原業主於2009年以307萬元購入單位，持貨16年，是次轉手賬面獲利453萬元離場，單位期內升值約148%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479361-%e9%a6%ac%e9%9e%8d%e5%b1%b1%e9%8a%80%e6%b9%96%ef%bc%8e%e5%a4%a9%e5%b3%b02%e6%88%bf-%e9%9b%b6%e8%ad%b0%e5%83%b9%e4%bb%a5760%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e7%8d%b2%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%b6%e6%89%bf%e6%8e%a5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 11:10:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
