            "title": "宏福苑五級火｜惠譽稱中國太平盈利受損",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">評級機構惠譽表示，大埔宏福苑火災預計將令到保險公司短期索償大增，並打擊宏福苑主要承保商中國太平保險(00966)的盈利。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">惠譽分析師預計，太平香港的綜合比率將「暫時上升」。綜合比率是保險公司評估日常營運表現的盈利能力指標。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">分析師估計公司會出現適度的資本侵蝕，但不太可能影響信用評級。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據外電本周初報道，太平保險（香港）已經為宏福苑完成首批9宗家居保險賠付，合共537萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15481885-%e5%ae%8f%e7%a6%8f%e8%8b%91%e4%ba%94%e7%b4%9a%e7%81%ab%ef%bd%9c%e6%83%a0%e8%ad%bd%e7%a8%b1%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%aa%e5%b9%b3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8f%97%e6%90%8d-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240326_FI_source-web_00966.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 11:00:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "兩新股跌二至三成  遇見小麵一手蝕920元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩新股大幅低開，現趺幅稍收窄，惟亦跌20%至30%，遇見小麵(02408)一手蝕920元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"天域半導體招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02658.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"天域半導體招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02658.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">天域半導體招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地中式麵館餐飲集團遇見小麵(02408)現跌26.14%，報5.2元，一手500股不計手續費蝕920元，今早開市報5元，較招股價7.04元，挫28.98%，為暫時低位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地碳化硅外延片製造商天域半導體(02658)現報44.6元，跌23.1%，一手50股不計手續費蝕670元  較招股價低34.48%，報38元，為暫時低位。開市報38元，較招股價58元，下挫34.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">遇見小麵集資淨額6.17億元。公開發售部分超額認購424.97倍，認購一手500股，中籤率2%；認購400手20萬股穩獲一手，保薦人招銀國際。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">天域半導體集資淨額約16.73億元。公開發售部分超額認購59.63倍，認購一手50股，中籤率10%。保薦人為中信証券。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15481824-%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e4%ba%8c%e8%87%b3%e4%b8%89%e6%88%90-%e9%81%87%e8%a6%8b%e5%b0%8f%e9%ba%b5%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e8%9d%95920%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250415_FI_source-web_Xiao-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 10:00:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
